message.harborInstall:
This installation uses a Harbor image repository deployed via Docker Compose, suitable for testing or basic use environments. It is not recommended for high-availability scenarios.
The installation requires a machine running Ubuntu 18.04, with the following minimum specifications:
• CPU: 4 cores
• Memory: 8 GB
• Disk: 200 GB
The actual resource requirements may vary depending on specific business workloads.
message.harborInstall1:
The offline and online installation commands can be executed directly on the host machine.
Note: The host must have the curl command installed.
• Offline installation uses prepackaged offline files, including docker-compose and Harbor components.
• Online installation pulls docker-compose and Harbor components from GitHub.
It is recommended to use the offline installation for better stability and control.

welcomePage.GPUCloudServerText: GPU cloud servers deliver exceptional parallel computing power, enabling a wide range of workloads such as AI training and inference, scientific computing, image processing, and video encoding/decoding.
welcomePage.bannerText1:
The emergence of large language models is driving a transformation in computing infrastructure. As edge computing rises, model inference is accelerating the shift of intelligence toward the edge.
ElasticCloud, independently developed by Lnjoying, is a full-stack intelligent computing operating system tailored for LLM workloads. It seamlessly integrates IaaS, PaaS, networking, and LLMOps capabilities to provide end-to-end AI cloud solutions and services.
welcomePage.bannerText2:
The emergence of large language models is driving a transformation in computing infrastructure. As edge computing rises, model inference is accelerating the shift of intelligence toward the edge.
ElasticCloud, independently developed by Lnjoying, is a full-stack intelligent computing operating system tailored for LLM workloads. It seamlessly integrates IaaS, PaaS, networking, and LLMOps capabilities to provide end-to-end AI cloud solutions and services.
welcomePage.bannerText4: Unlocking the Full Power of Innovation
welcomePage.bannerTitle1: An All-in-One GPU Cloud Platform Powering Limitless AI Potential
welcomePage.bannerTitle2: Building Global Intelligent Infrastructure to Accelerate the Digital Revolution
welcomePage.bannerTitle3: Partner with 91GPU — Join 91GPU as a Service Partner
welcomePage.bannerTitle4: Delivering High-Performance Engines for AI Models
welcomePage.helpAIInnovation: Driving AI Innovation, Building a Smarter Future
welcomePage.ourServiceText: Empowering AI and Big Data Innovation with Stable, High-Efficiency Compute from 91GPU
welcomePage.ourServiceText1: Unified access and management of diverse computing resources, including bare metal and GPUs, with high scalability and stability.
welcomePage.ourServiceText2: Intelligent orchestration and automated deployment to boost application efficiency and ensure resource utilization.
welcomePage.ourServiceText3: Cross-region resource pooling and dynamic task distribution to support large-scale, flexible compute sharing.
welcomePage.ourServiceText4: Secure and private storage for public and individual use, with full support for upload, download, and data isolation.
welcomePage.ourServiceText5: High-speed, encrypted file transfer with breakpoint resume, powered by proprietary acceleration technology.
welcomePage.ourServiceText6: Continuous backup, remote sync, and disaster recovery to ensure data safety and business continuity.
welcomePage.ourServiceText7: Full-lifecycle management of computing services, with real-time monitoring, flexible billing, and operational analytics.
welcomePage.ourServiceText8: Multi-dimensional system monitoring with auto alerting, fault self-healing, and resource isolation to guarantee platform stability.
